ic effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/87706/', '', 'Lidocaine, Tetracaine, Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Trimethobenzamide, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', '', 1767369485);
